{"tid":1504723,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[重要]屌頭先後排無啦啦set RB嗰班！","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T13:44:19.000Z","uid":96371,"like":89,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f248cd8ff97e0da501e8c7647181fdd64265b488","tid":1504723,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:27:35.000Z","msg":"先利申我垃圾早走撚<br />\n六點半倒走行原路上番葵盛葵芳嗰條斜路，大約過左加里同信興中心，有個露天停車場嗰度<br />\n無啦啦見到好撚整齊十鳩幾層水馬膠馬RB<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你地呀！前面仲有千鳩幾個手足未走架！</span></span></span><br />\n想唔想像到大棚手足如果上到黎，前有RB，後有黑狗會係點情況呀！係陷家產呀！！<br />\n當時同另外幾個手足一路講後面大把人未走一路幫手拉番開<br />\n仲有人話放疏啲咪得大家識走<br />\n屌啦咁你不如咪撚放，手足識轉彎唔通狗真係弱智咩？前排俾你咁kick一kick咪又慢左俾人拉多幾個<br />\n<br />\n麻煩中後排退緊時有咩動作前都盡量了解下前線，諗清楚先啦！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你地退先係為左有足夠空間俾前線暢順地走<br />\n唔係set番RB黎阻撤退手足啊！</span>"},{"pid":"3b91b439691e9ead861b879f25d5193d07229e5f","tid":1504723,"uid":96371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"會累死人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22923733ade79b54bc6b5537b03200c11a32adb0","tid":1504723,"uid":96371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"諗清楚先行動啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ed86c7c92aa5250dcf4a78164e8f1b9e0c7383","tid":1504723,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"066dcbefb251625e254676c5deeb66a84825d2d8","tid":1504723,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"913940d70d3af4673e92c493e5eb0b8a4e9edcd3","tid":1504723,"uid":96371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"希望你地只係好心做錯事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4347b808e60233d93660d2e69edc813